videos.description: Fabian White Jr. elevates for a big block for Houston, which leads to Josh Carlton dropping in a layup at the other end.

videos.description: Houston's Kyler Edwards drops in a trio of clutch 3-pointers in the second half as the Cougars pull off the upset against No. 1 Arizona to advance to the Elite Eight.
